metadata.name: Ape King #1
metadata.description: Welcome to the Journey of the Reborn Ape King. Throughout this dynamic storytelling collection, we present a set of 10,000 Ape King collectibles expressing the extraordinary journey of Sun Wu Kong from long years of spiritual cultivation and rebels against the primacy of heaven. Our collection describes the journey of the Ape King with a set of 72 transformation skills that Sun Wu Kong inherits and quickly masters a set of secret oral formulas. These abilities have given him the ability to live through the three calamities of thunder, fire, and wind.
